node.text: #ad Nothin’ better than having a special bond with your bestie like these Frozen 2 Anna and Elsa singing dolls from @hasbro! They are SO lucky to have each other!  I might not have a sister yet...😜but I have special bonds with each of my besties!  Tag YOUR besties in a comment below! Ok...bye! #Hasbro #frozen2 #disney

...the day I met Everleigh’s new baby sister for the first time! 
Happy 2nd Birthday Posie Rayne - from Ava!
